#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:28
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Bookmarks</"
#| "guimenuitem> </menuchoice> option opens the <guilabel>Bookmark Editor</"
#| "guilabel>."
msgid ""
"In many applications (&eg; &konqueror;, &konsole;, &konversation;) the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit Bookmarks</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> option opens the <guilabel>Bookmark Editor</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Meniu punktas <menuchoice><guimenu>Žymelės</guimenu><guimenuitem>Redaguoti "
"žymeles</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> atidaro <guilabel>Žymelių redaktorių</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively you can launch the editor as standalone application to edit "
"the browser bookmarks."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:34
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This shows a tree view of your bookmarks and bookmark subfolders. As is "
#| "usual for tree views in &kde;, subfolders are shown with a small square "
#| "at the left of the folder name; if the square contains a <keycap>+</"
#| "keycap> sign <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on it will expand "
#| "the view to show the contents of that subfolder and the <keycap>+</"
#| "keycap> sign will change to <keycap>-</keycap>, <mousebutton>left</"
#| "mousebutton> clicking on the <keycap>-</keycap> sign will collapse the "
#| "subfolder view."
msgid ""
"The editor shows a tree view of your bookmarks and bookmark subfolders. As "
"is usual for tree views in &kde;, subfolders are shown with a small "
"<keycap>&gt;</keycap> arrow at the left of the folder name; "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on it will expand the view to show "
"the contents of that subfolder and the <keycap>&gt;</keycap> arrow will "
"change to <keycap>v</keycap>; <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> clicking on "
"the <keycap>v</keycap> arrow will collapse the subfolder view."
msgstr ""
"Čia rodoma jūsų žymelių bei žymelių aplankų hierarchija. Kaip ir kitose "
"&kde; programose, medžio pavidalo hierarhijos poaplankiai rodomi su "
"nedideliu kvadračiuku prie aplanko pavadinimo. Jei kvadračiuke rodomas "
"<keycap>+</keycap>, reiškia paspaudus <mousebutton>kairįjį</mousebutton> "
"pelės mygtuką šaka bus išskleista parodant aplanko turinį, ženkliukas "
"<keycap>+</keycap> pasikeis į <keycap>-</keycap>. Dar kartą paspaudus "
"<mousebutton>kairįjį</mousebutton> mygtuką and <keycap>-</keycap> ženkliuko "
"poaplankis bus suskleistas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:42
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To select an item in the list you can <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> "
#| "click on it, or you can navigate through the list by using the <keysym> "
#| "Up arrow</keysym> and <keysym>Down arrow</keysym> keys to move around, "
#| "<keysym>Right arrow</keysym> to expand a subfolder and <keysym> Left "
#| "arrow</keysym> to collapse it."
msgid ""
"To select an item in the list you can <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> click "
"on it, or you can navigate through the list by using the <keysym>Up</keysym> "
"and <keysym>Down</keysym> keys to move around, <keysym>Right</keysym> to "
"expand a subfolder and <keysym>Left</keysym> to collapse it."
msgstr ""
"Norimą žymelę galite pasirinkti arba <mousebutton>kairiuoju</mousebutton> "
"pelės mygtuku, arba klavišais <keysym>Aukštyn</keysym> ir <keysym>Žemyn</"
"keysym>. Aplankų išskleidimui naudokite <keysym>Dešinėn</keysym>, o "
"suskleidimui – <keysym>Kairėn</keysym>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can move an item to a different place in the list by using the normal "
"Drag and Drop or <guimenuitem>Cut</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem> Paste</"
"guimenuitem> methods. The order in which the items appear in the "
"<guilabel>Bookmark Editor</guilabel> is the order they will appear in the "
"<guimenu>Bookmarks</guimenu> drop down list. The <menuchoice><guimenu>Folder "
"</guimenu><guimenuitem>Insert Separator</guimenuitem></menuchoice> option "
"can be used to insert separating lines into the list wherever you wish."
msgstr ""
"Žymelę galite perkelti į kitą aplanką arba ją pertempdami, arba naudodami "
"standartinį <guimenuitem>Iškirpimo</guimenuitem> ir <guimenuitem>Įkėlimo</"
"guimenuitem> metodą. Kokia eilės tvarka žymelės sudėliotos <guilabel>Žymelių "
"redaktoriuje</guilabel>, tokia tvarka jie ir pasirodys <guimenu>Žymelių</"
"guimenu> meniu. Norėdami įterpti žymeles atskiriančias linijas – skirtukus, "
"naudokite meniu punktą <menuchoice><guimenu>Aplankas</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Įterpti skirtuką</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A new subfolder can be created at the selected point in the list by using "
"the <guimenuitem>New Folder...</guimenuitem> option in the <guimenu>Folder</"
"guimenu> menu or from the drop down menu you get when you "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on an item in the main part of the "
"window, or with <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></"
"keycombo>"
msgstr ""
"Naują aplanką galite sukurti parinkę <guimenuitem>Naujas aplankas...</"
"guimenuitem> iš meniu <guimenu>Aplankas</guimenu> arba iš kontekstinio meniu "
"paspaudus <mousebutton>dešinį</mousebutton> pelės mygtuką arba tiesiog "
"paspaudę <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>N</keycap></keycombo>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the name of a bookmark or folder select it then press <keycap>F2</"
"keycap> or choose the <guimenuitem>Rename</guimenuitem> item from the "
"<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu or the pop up menu that appears when you "
"<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> click on the item. Similarly, you can edit "
"the &URL; by pressing <keycap>F3</keycap> or choosing the <guimenuitem> "
"Change Location</guimenuitem> menu item."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami pakeisti žymelės ar aplanko pavadinimą, pažymėkite jį ir spauskite "
"<keycap>F2</keycap> arba pasirinkite <guimenuitem>Pervadinti</guimenuitem> "
"iš meniu <guimenu>Keisti</guimenu> arba kontekstinio meniu, parodomo "
"paspaudus <mousebutton>dešinį</mousebutton> pelės mygtuką. Žymelės nuorodą "
"(&URL;) galite keisti atitinkamai paspaudę <keycap>F3</keycap> arba iš meniu "
"pasirinkę <guimenuitem>Pakeisti URL</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The <guilabel>Bookmark Editor</guilabel> lets you import bookmarks from a "
#| "range of other browsers into &konqueror;'s bookmark list, putting them "
#| "into a new folder or replacing all current bookmarks. To do this select "
#| "<guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> from the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. "
#| "The <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export</guisubmenu> </"
#| "menuchoice> option can be used to export &konqueror;'s bookmarks to a "
#| "&Netscape; or Mozilla browser."
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Bookmark Editor</guilabel> lets you import bookmarks from a "
"range of other browsers into &konqueror;'s bookmark list, putting them into "
"a new folder or replacing all current bookmarks. To do this select "
"<guisubmenu>Import</guisubmenu> from the <guimenu>File</guimenu> menu. The "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> option can be used to export &konqueror;'s bookmarks to a "
"Mozilla browser."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Žymelių redaktoriumi</guilabel> galite įkelti žymeles iš eilės "
"kitų naršyklių į &konqueror; žymelių sąrašo naują katalogą arba pakeičiant "
"visas esamas žymeles. Kad tą padarytumėte, iš meniu <guimenu>Failas</"
"guimenu> parinkite <guisubmenu>Importuoti</guisubmenu>. Meniu punktas "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Failas</guimenu><guisubmenu>Eksportuoti</guisubmenu></"
"menuchoice> leidžia eksportuoti &konqueror; žymeles į &Netscape; ar Mozilla "
"naršykles."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To select which bookmark subfolder is used to hold the Bookmark Toolbar "
"items select the subfolder then choose <guimenuitem>Set as Toolbar Folder</"
"guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Folder</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Norėdami nurodyti, kuris žymelių poaplankis rodomas žymelių įrankinėje, "
"pažymėkite poaplankį ir iš meniu <guimenu>Aplankas</guimenu> parinkite "
"punktą <guimenuitem>Nustatyti įrankių juostos aplanku</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are tidying up your bookmarks and have forgotten what a particular "
"web page is, you can easily open it from within the <guilabel> Bookmark "
"Editor</guilabel> by <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> clicking on the item "
"and selecting <guimenuitem>Open in Konqueror</guimenuitem> from the pop up "
"menu. If you just want to check that the &URL; is still valid select "
"<guimenuitem>Check Status</guimenuitem> instead."
msgstr ""
"Jei tvarkote savo žymeles ir pamiršote, koks yra kuris nors puslapis, galite "
"patogiai jį atidaryti tiesiai iš <guilabel>žymelių redaktoriaus</guilabel> "
"spausdami <mousebutton>dešinį</mousebutton> pelės mygtuką ir iš konteksinio "
"meniu pasirinkdami <guimenuitem>Atverti su Konqueror</guimenuitem>. Jei "
"tiesiog norite patikrinti, ar nuoroda vis dar galioja, parinkite "
"<guimenuitem>Tikrinti būvį</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All your changes are automatically saved if you close the <guilabel>Bookmark "
"Editor</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Visi pakeitimai automatiškai išsaugomi uždarius <guilabel>Žymelių "
"redaktorių</guilabel>."

